<inglise> (2) the system for sizing asparagus should be simplified to make it compatible with developments in production and marketing conditions, especially as regards wholesale and consumer requirements. </inglise>
<eesti> 2) spargli suuruse m&auml;&auml;ramise s&uuml;steemi tuleks lihtsustada, et see oleks koosk&otilde;las tootmise ja turustamise tingimuste arenguga, eriti hulgim&uuml;&uuml;gi ja tarbijate n&otilde;udmistega. </eesti>
